&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a procurement leader to help strengthen the procurement function, manage client facing opportunities, and scale the next generation of AI-enabled procurement solutions. This role sits at the intersection of procurement, product development, and client engagement, applying deep domain expertise to shape how our solutions perform in real-world environments.&lt;/p&gt;
